8. Data Preprocessing in R
Handling missing values: na.omit(data)


Renaming columns: names(data) <- c("A", "B", "C")


Subsetting data: data[data$age > 20, ]


Normalization: scale(data$column)


 9. Data Visualization in R
âž¤ Basic Plot:
plot(data$Height, data$Weight)
âž¤ Histogram:
hist(data$Age)
âž¤ Using ggplot2:
library(ggplot2)
ggplot(data, aes(x=Height, y=Weight)) + geom_point()
 10. Packages in R
Packages extend the functionality of R. They can be installed from CRAN.
âž¤ Install and Load:
